{"type":null,"faqId":46092,"title":"WLAN无法连接到路由器怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.108333334in;margin-bottom:0.108333334in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.5416667in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1、若 WLAN 热点为加密热点，请您确认密码是否输入正确，注意区分大小写。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、请确认 WLAN 热点名称或密码是否发生了变更，重新搜索要连接的热点，输入正确的密码后连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、请将手机置于 WLAN 热点的有效距离内，距离太远会使网络信号变弱，导致网络连接自动断开。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4、WLAN 热点可能已达到最大连接数，请尝试连接其他的可用网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>5、若连接 WLAN 热点时一直显示正在获取 IP 地址，请按照以下操作设置静态 IP：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>若是加密热点，在 WLAN 设置界面，点击要连接的热点名称。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在弹出的对话框勾选“显示高级选项”，在“IP设置”区域点击下拉菜单，选择“静态”，手动输入 IP 地址和域名等信息。输入密码，然后点击“连接”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170734\" style=\"width:1.8548611in;height:3.3in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>若是开放热点，在 WLAN 设置界面，长按要连接的热点名称。在弹出的选项菜单中，点击“修改网络”。在弹出的对话框中，勾选“显示高级选项”，在“IP设置”区域点击下拉菜单，选择“静态”，手动输入IP 地址和域名等信息后保存。连接成功后，状态栏会显示 WLAN 图标。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170735\" style=\"width:2.1069446in;height:3.74375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>  </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170736\" style=\"width:2.1069446in;height:3.7430556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>6、请检查无线路由器是否开启 MAC 地址过滤功能。如果开启此功能，不在接入列表中的手机无法接入 WLAN 网络。详细设置方法请参考路由器说明书。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>7、某些公共 WLAN 热点可能需要在网页端登录连接，详情请咨询 WLAN 热点提供商。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>若问题依然存在，请重新打开 WLAN 开关或重启 WLAN 热点。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1872","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444376107000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":17,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"WLAN,Wifi,无线网络,路由器,连不上","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}